{"data":[{"date":"14:51 16/06","title":"L\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u l\u00e0m BLV b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Fabregas b\u1ecb ch\u00ea nh\u01b0 ... b\u1ed3i b\u00e0n","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/lan-dau-lam-blv-bong-da-tien-ve-fabregas-bi-che-nhu-boi-ban.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Fabregas \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i trong bu\u1ed5i b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn tr\u1eadn T\u00e2y Ban Nha h\u00f2a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n TBN d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 nh\u01b0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Fabregas c\u0169ng \u0103n ng\u1ee7 v\u1edbi tr\u00e1i b\u00f3ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y v\u1edbi vai tr\u00f2 b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a BBC Sport.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00eam qua, Cesc Fabregas \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi vai tr\u00f2 b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn vi\u00ean \u1edf tr\u1eadn TBN \u2013 B\u0110N. Trong l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0m BLV, Cesc Fabregas \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i t\u1ed3i v\u00e0 cho th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 n\u0103ng khi\u1ebfu b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/NINTCHDBPICT000413675688.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Fabregas b\u1ecb n\u00e9m \u0111\u00e1 d\u1eef d\u1ed9i tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i v\u00ec ch\u1ecdn m\u1eb7c trang ph\u1ee5c ch\u1eb3ng gi\u1ed1ng ai xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh. Trang ph\u1ee5c nh\u01b0 th\u1ec3 \u201cthanh tra s\u1edf thu\u1ebf\u201d, \u201cV\u0110V \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eadt\u201d, \u201cB\u1ed3i b\u00e0n\u201d v\u00e0 \u201cTh\u00e0nh vi\u00ean qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed9i\u201d n\u00e0y m\u00e0 Fabregas b\u1ecb ch\u1ebf gi\u1ec5u r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cFabregas m\u1eb7c nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t \u1edf l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0m b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn vi\u00ean\u201d, Alex Young \u2714 @alexwsyoung ch\u00ea bai Fabregas.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cFabregas m\u1eb7c ch\u1eb3ng kh\u00e1c m\u1ed9t nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean so\u00e1t v\u00e9 xe bus\u201d, WorldCupMemories*@worldcupwillys ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cFabregas m\u1eb7c t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a De Gea \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa TBN v\u00e0 B\u0110N\u201d, Nick Maslin @Nick_Maslin m\u1ec9a mai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cFabregas m\u1eb7c nh\u01b0 anh b\u1ed3i b\u00e0n \u1edf nh\u00e0 h\u00e0ng\u201d, Richard Rooney@C_RRooney n\u00f3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 4 trong h\u00e0ng tr\u0103m b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn ch\u1ebf gi\u1ec5u Fabregas v\u00ec trang ph\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Chelsea \u1edf bu\u1ed5i b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn \u0111\u00eam qua.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3665","checkdouble":"188639"},{"date":"09:56 17/06","title":"Vua b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Maradona b\u1ecb c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c \u1edf tr\u1eadn Argentina vs Iceland","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/6/vua-bong-da-maradona-bi-cao-buoc-phan-biet-chung-toc-o-tran-argentina-vs-iceland.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \"Albiceleste\" b\u1ecb cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \"c\u1eed ch\u1ec9 ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng\" v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c khi d\u1ef1 kh\u00e1n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Lionel Messi.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">C\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 CLB Napoli \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0n v\u00e0 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 1-1 c\u1ee7a Argentina tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland. Tuy nhi\u00ean, s\u1ebd ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 nh\u00e0 b\u00e1o Jacqui Oatley c\u1ee7a BBC, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u1ee5 tr\u00e1ch \u0111\u01b0a tin tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 Maradona l\u00ean trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i Twitter.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Maradona ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c \u1edf tr\u1eadn Argentina vs Iceland h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Maradona ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c \u1edf tr\u1eadn Argentina vs Iceland h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/Maradona-phan-biet-chung-toc-o-tran-Argentina-vs-Iceland-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Hai nh\u00e0 b\u00e1o \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 vi\u1ec7c ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng pitch di\u1ec5n ra tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Spartak. \u1ea2nh: Twitter.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nOatley cho bi\u1ebft: \"M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 h\u00e9t l\u00ean 'Diego' v\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 n\u1edf m\u1ed9t n\u1ee5 c\u01b0\u1eddi, d\u00e0nh cho h\u1ecd m\u1ed9t n\u1ee5 h\u00f4n gi\u00f3 v\u00e0 v\u1eaby tay tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ngo\u1ea3nh m\u1eb7t quay \u0111i trong m\u1ed9t c\u1eed ch\u1ec9 ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Oatley l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 b\u00e1o Seema Jaswal c\u0169ng ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a Maradona ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Spartak v\u00e0 x\u00e1c th\u1ef1c th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y.\"T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 v\u00e0 th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 cho\u00e1ng v\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng n\u00e0y\", c\u00f4 n\u00f3i th\u00eam. D\u00f2ng tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i n\u00e0y sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ea7n 3.000 l\u01b0\u1ee3t chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nJaswall cho bi\u1ebft: \"T\u00f4i ng\u1ed3i ngay c\u1ea1nh Jacqui v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a Maradona. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y n\u00ean c\u01b0 x\u1eed \u0111\u00fang m\u1ef1c h\u01a1n. Nh\u1eefng ch\u00e0ng trai ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea5m h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u1ea5y v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u1ecd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Th\u1eadt \u0111\u00e1ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nLeo Messi c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p t\u1ea1i World Cup n\u0103m nay khi \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia c\u1ee7a anh ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland c\u1ee7a HLV Heimir Hallgrimsson.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\"Albiceleste\" s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp theo v\u1edbi Croatia v\u00e0o r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 22/6 t\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Nigeria \u1edf lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng t\u1ea1i VCK World Cup 2018 sau \u0111\u00f3 5 ng\u00e0y.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3664","checkdouble":"188701"},{"date":"09:38 17/06","title":"HLV \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i vi\u1ec7c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/16/hlv-duc-thang-ly-giai-viec-tin-tuong-thu-mon-bui-tien-dung-o-tran-gap-can-tho.jpeg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 chi\u1ec1u 16/6, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a FLC Thanh H\u00f3a \u0111\u00e3 l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i vi\u1ec7c \u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n tr\u1ebb B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh.</h2><h2>HLV \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng tin t\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng v\u00ec c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u cao t\u1ed1t</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1edbm nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 chi\u1ec1u qua, CLB FLC Thanh H\u00f3a \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i th\u1ee9 hai li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi c\u00f9ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-0 nh\u1edd b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Tr\u1ecdng Ho\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi \u1edf ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y, HLV \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 d\u00f9 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf v\u00ec l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7c.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i vi\u1ec7c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i vi\u1ec7c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/30/HLV-Duc-Thang-ly-giai-viec-tin-tuong-thu-mon-Bui-Tien-Dung-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng chia s\u1ebb l\u00fd do tin t\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng\u00a0</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n tr\u1ebb B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u, thay th\u1ebf ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n anh B\u1eedu Ng\u1ecdc d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. V\u00e0 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi x\u1ee9 T\u00e2y \u0110\u00f4.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen t\u1eeb \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng. L\u00fd gi\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, v\u1ecb t\u00e2n thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng FLC Thanh H\u00f3a cho bi\u1ebft: Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n quan s\u00e1t k\u0129 s\u1ebd th\u1ea5y, B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u cao h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi Thanh Th\u1eafng. L\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1, n\u00f3 ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o ngo\u1ea1i binh, ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng.\u00a0 <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng v\u1edbi l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf chi\u1ec1u cao s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Thanh Th\u1eafng. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, h\u00f4m nay Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ee9u thua cho FLC Thanh H\u00f3a. Nh\u00ecn chung h\u00f4m nay, t\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00ean s\u00e2n\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, HLV \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng v\u1eabn y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. C\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Th\u1ec3 C\u00f4ng n\u00f3i th\u00eam: \u201c\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 r\u1ea5t \u00fd ngh\u0129a cho to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c, t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung cao nh\u1ea5t, h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i\u201d..<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">FLC Thanh H\u00f3a sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng 7 v\u1edbi 19 \u0111i\u1ec3m. \u1ede v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 22/6, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Becamex B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-sai-gon-vs-ha-noi-19h00-ngay-176-vleague-2018-168-188690.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/nhan-dinh-sai-gon-vs-ha-noi-19h00-ngay-176-vleague-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-sai-gon-vs-ha-noi-19h00-ngay-176-vleague-2018-168-188690.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh S\u00e0i G\u00f2n vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i 19h00 ng\u00e0y 17/6 (V-League 2018)</span><br>\r\nS\u00e0i G\u00f2n vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i l\u00fac 19h00 ng\u00e0y 17/6 (V\u00f2ng 14 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n,...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-shb-da-nang-vs-hagl-17h00-ngay-176-tim-lai-chien-thang-168-188684.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/nhan-dinh-shb-da-nang-vs-hagl-17h00-ngay-176-tim-lai-chien-thang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-shb-da-nang-vs-hagl-17h00-ngay-176-tim-lai-chien-thang-168-188684.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs HAGL (17h00 ng\u00e0y 17/6): T\u00ecm l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng</span><br>\r\nC\u1ea3 SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs HAGL \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Do \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p nhau n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:#081f2c;=\"\" mso-fareast-language:ko\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3663","checkdouble":"188698"},{"date":"08:08 17/06","title":"T\u1eeb gi\u1edd, h\u00e3y g\u1ecdi Messi l\u00e0 \"Miss Penalty\"","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/17/tu-gio-hay-goi-messi-la-miss-penalty.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u1eddi ch\u1ebf nh\u1ea1o v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch s\u00e2u cay nh\u1ea5t d\u00e0nh cho si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018.</h2>Lionel Messi \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn sau khi \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n, khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i chia \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi Iceland \u1edf tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n World Cup 2018. V\u00ec qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n h\u1ecfng \u0103n n\u00e0y, Messi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ec1 t\u00e0i b\u1ecb d\u00e2n m\u1ea1ng ch\u1ebf \u1ea3nh v\u00e0 nh\u1ea1o b\u00e1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong \u0111\u00f3, \"th\u00e2m nho\" nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 l\u00e0n s\u00f3ng k\u00eau g\u1ecdi \u0111\u1eb7t bi\u1ec7t danh m\u1edbi cho Messi l\u00e0 \"Miss Penalty\" (t\u1eeb Miss trong ti\u1ebfng Anh c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 hoa h\u1eadu v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ngh\u0129a kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1).\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/df0lw64waaaosbc-1529164555361572184660-15291646284422035025288.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/3538019017140834453410524149379513962201088n-15291646406571170844120.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i ra c\u00e1c fan c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng kh\u1ecfi so s\u00e1nh Messi v\u00e0 Ronaldo. M\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp hattrick, gi\u00fap B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 3-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc T\u00e2y Ban Nha m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd. Trong khi ng\u01b0\u1eddi kia th\u1eadm ch\u00ed s\u00fat h\u1ecfng penalty (c\u1ea7n nh\u1edb r\u1eb1ng 1/3 b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Ronaldo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean ... ch\u1ea5m 11m).\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/4-1529163972539832576147.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Messi b\u1ecb ch\u1ebf nh\u1ea1o sau khi s\u00fat h\u1ecfng 11m tr\u1eadn Argentina 1-1 Iceland h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Messi b\u1ecb ch\u1ebf nh\u1ea1o sau khi s\u00fat h\u1ecfng 11m tr\u1eadn Argentina 1-1 Iceland h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/Messi-bi-che-nhao-sau-khi-sut-hong-11m-tran-Argentina-1-1-Iceland-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ronaldo: s\u00fat penalty th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n, l\u1eadp hat-trick. Messi: h\u1ecfng penalty, h\u1ecfng v\u00e0i c\u00fa s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp, kh\u00f4ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t fan kh\u00e1c th\u00ec ch\u1ebf nh\u1ea1o b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch vi\u1ebft l\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i Twitter, k\u00e8m theo t\u1ea5m h\u00ecnh Messi \u0111ang k\u00fd l\u00ean m\u1ed9t t\u1edd gi\u1ea5y v\u1edbi n\u1ed9i dung: \"Ch\u00e0o Ronaldo. T\u1edb l\u00e0 Messi \u0111\u00e2y. T\u1edb \u0111ang b\u0103n kho\u0103n kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft l\u00e0m th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n nh\u1ec9? H\u00e3y ph\u1ea3n h\u1ed3i s\u1edbm cho t\u1edb nh\u00e9\".\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/Screen-Shot-2018-06-17-at-1-39-3258-6509-1529177580.png.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ed1ng k\u00ea cho th\u1ea5y Messi \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng b\u1ed1n trong b\u1ea3y qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t (cho Barca v\u00e0 Argentina), t\u1ee9c l\u00e0 t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 h\u1ecfng \u0103n l\u00ean t\u1edbi 57%. Danh th\u1ee7 Gary Lineker vi\u1ebft l\u00ean Twitter: \"Messi b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n. C\u00f9ng th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m, Ronaldo c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111ang nh\u00e1y m\u1eaft tinh ngh\u1ecbch\". <br>\r\n<br>\r\nSi\u00eau sao Argentina tung ra t\u1edbi 11 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf tr\u1eadn ho\u00e0 Iceland 1-1, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n ghi b\u00e0n. Trong khi Ronaldo ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n b\u1ed1n pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 hat-trick v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2010 - T\u00e2y Ban Nha.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ve mat cua Cristiano Ronaldo khi nghe tin Messi vua da hong 1 qua 11 m\" title=\"V\u1ebb m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo khi nghe tin Messi v\u1eeba \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng 1 qu\u1ea3 11 m\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/3_4.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">V\u1ebb m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo khi nghe tin Messi v\u1eeba \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng 1 qu\u1ea3 11 m</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3661","checkdouble":"188688"},{"date":"07:20 17/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs HAGL (17h00 ng\u00e0y 17/6): T\u00ecm l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/nhan-dinh-shb-da-nang-vs-hagl-17h00-ngay-176-tim-lai-chien-thang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ea3 SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs HAGL \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Do \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p nhau n\u00e0y.</h2><br>\r\n<h2>Ch\u1ee7 l\u1ea5n kh\u00e1ch</h2>\r\n<h2><o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng trong n\u0103m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i Nguy\u1ec5n Minh Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc sau giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua chu\u1ed7i 5 tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi k\u1ebft th\u00fac l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i b\u1eb1ng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n oan \u1ee9c tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Thanh H\u00f3a. Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u00e1ng l\u1ebd ra \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u00f4ng H\u00e0n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m, khi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng h\u1ee3p l\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o nh\u1eadp t\u1ecbch \u0110\u1ed7 Merlo l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn do b\u1ecb tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i bi\u00ean c\u0103ng c\u1edd vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thua tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00f3, \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb k\u00ecm ch\u00e2n \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed gi\u1eefa BXH. V\u00ec v\u1eady, h\u1ecd hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf tr\u1eadn SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs HAGL chi\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd c\u00e0ng l\u00e0m cho t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh tr\u1edf n\u00ean kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u01a1n.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs HAGL (17h00 ng\u00e0y 176) T\u00ecm l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn th h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs HAGL (17h00 ng\u00e0y 176) T\u00ecm l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn th h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/cff9c17ef0911f2c775cdecac76d84bf_L.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc HAGL tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p nhau v\u1edbi th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i chung cu\u1ed9c 2-0 thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai, tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch to\u00e0n th\u1eafng Gia Lai t\u1ea1i \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Minh Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n m\u01a1 t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00f4n l\u1ee9a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn c\u1ea3 3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong c\u00e1c chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch \u1edf \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng. \u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00ean thi \u0111\u1ea5u chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, l\u1ee9a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u00f4ng H\u00e0n v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-2. V\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u1edf hai m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i sau \u0111\u00f3 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c k\u1ebft c\u1ee5c l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00e0 1-3 v\u00e0 0-1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec th\u1ebf, khi s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, CLB SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn s\u00f2ng ph\u1eb3ng v\u1edbi HAGL, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch c\u0169ng \u0111ang t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>G\u1ed7 t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng, \u1edf v\u00f2ng 13 V-League di\u1ec5n ra gi\u1eefa tu\u1ea7n v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, CLB HAGL c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c 2-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam. Hai l\u1ea7n v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi c\u00e1c pha ghi b\u00e0n v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u thi\u1ebfu ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 b\u1eb1ng 3 b\u00e0n thua sau \u0111\u00f3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn thua n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn &lsquo;G\u1ed7&rsquo; b\u1ecb c\u1eaft m\u1ea1ch 9 tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb t\u1ee5t h\u1ea1ng khi xu\u1ed1ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 8 \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf tr\u1eadn t\u1edbi, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai s\u1ebd kh\u00f3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i trong t\u1ed1p 5 nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1eebng k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs HAGL (17h00 ng\u00e0y 176) T\u00ecm l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn th h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs HAGL (17h00 ng\u00e0y 176) T\u00ecm l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn th h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/hagl.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HAGL ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u0169ng \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1, CLB HAGL s\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3n s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eebng b\u1ecb b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c treo gi\u00f2 h\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i v\u00ec c\u00f3 h\u00e0nh vi v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o v\u1edbi Duy M\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC. \u0110\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft c\u1ee7a &lsquo;G\u1ed7&rsquo; khi m\u00e0 h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i v\u1eeba b\u1ecb m\u1ea5t trung v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n H\u1ea1nh c\u00f3 \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t ngu\u1ed9i c\u1ea5m thi \u0111\u1ea5u 3 tr\u1eadn.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u00f4ng H\u00e0n l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t khi thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0110\u1ed7 Thanh Th\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Minh T\u00e2m do th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3 vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 V\u00f5 Huy To\u00e0n t\u00e1i ph\u00e1t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1eabu sao SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o ngo\u1ea1i binh \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, \u0110\u1ed7 Merlo lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 duy\u00ean ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi HAGL. V\u00e0 bi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e2u trong m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb9p tr\u1eddi, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c x\u1ea3y \u0111\u1ebfn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00e0n so t\u00e0i gi\u1eefa&nbsp;SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs HAGL s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 17h00 chi\u1ec1u nay 17/6 v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng tr\u00ean k\u00eanh VTV5. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Bongda24h t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp, mong b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd theo d\u00f5i.</p>\r\n<h2>Th\u00f4ng tin l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng:<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng: \u0110\u1ed7 Thanh Th\u1ecbnh, Ho\u00e0ng Minh T\u00e2m v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t do th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t. Huy To\u00e0n ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HAGL: Nguy\u1ec5n V\u1eafng H\u1ea1nh v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t do nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ee7 3 th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng: Thanh B\u00ecnh, Ti\u1ebfn D\u1ee5ng, \u0110\u1ed7 Merlo, Nh\u1eadt T\u00e2n, \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh, Thanh H\u1ea3i, Ng\u1ecdc Th\u1eafng, Diogo, \u0110\u1ee9c L\u1ec5, Anh Quang, V\u0103n Th\u1eafng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HAGL: V\u0103n Ti\u1ebfn, \u0110\u1ee9c L\u01b0\u01a1ng, \u0110\u00f4ng Tri\u1ec1u, Kim Jin-seo, V\u0103n Thanh, H\u1ed3ng Duy, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng,&nbsp;Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, Rimario, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, V\u0103n To\u00e0n.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n: 2-1&nbsp;</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/vong-14-vleague-2018-lieu-suc-nong-co-giam-mua-world-cup-168-188647.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/14/vong-14-vleague-2018-lieu-suc-nong-co-giam-mua-world-cup.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/vong-14-vleague-2018-lieu-suc-nong-co-giam-mua-world-cup-168-188647.html\">V\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018: Li\u1ec7u s\u1ee9c n\u00f3ng c\u00f3 gi\u1ea3m m\u00f9a World Cup?</span><br>\r\nV\u00f2ng 14 V-League di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u00edt nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a NHM trong th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m World Cup 2018 \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra. Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1eabn c\u00f3...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3660","checkdouble":"188684"},{"date":"07:51 17/06","title":"B\u1ecb c\u1eaft m\u1ea1ch b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, HAGL th\u1eaft ch\u1eb7t k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt m\u00f9a World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/14/hagl-that-chat-ky-luat-mua-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 n\u00fai HAGL m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng quy \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1ea5t nghi\u00eam ng\u1eb7t m\u00f9a World Cup nh\u1eb1m h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1ee9c khuya xem b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c.</h2><h2>HAGL th\u1eaft ch\u1eb7t k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt m\u00f9a World Cup 2018</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">VCK World Cup 2018 di\u1ec5n ra tr\u00f9ng v\u1edbi th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG V-League b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o giai \u0111o\u1ea1n c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng nh\u1ea5t. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng bi\u1ec7n ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1eeba chung vui xem World Cup v\u1eeba \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, t\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1ee3t CLB HAGL c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u201cthi\u1ebft qu\u00e2n lu\u1eadt\u201d trong th\u1eddi gian di\u1ec5n ra World Cup 2018. Theo \u0111\u00f3, HAGL c\u1ea5m tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i th\u1ee9c khuya xem b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 sinh ho\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1eabn theo khu\u00f4n ph\u00e9p b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HAGL th\u1eaft ch\u1eb7t k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt m\u00f9a World Cup 2018  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HAGL th\u1eaft ch\u1eb7t k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt m\u00f9a World Cup 2018  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/3/HAGL-that-chat-ky-luat-mua-World-Cup-2018--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL b\u1ecb c\u1ea5m th\u1ee9c khuya xem World Cup 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n Nguy\u1ec5n T\u1ea5n Anh c\u1ee7a CLB HAGL cho bi\u1ebft BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ec9 cho ph\u00e9p c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xem nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1edbm t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018: \u201cTr\u01b0\u1edbc khi World Cup 2018 kh\u1edfi tranh, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1eafng nghe nguy\u1ec7n v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. \u0110a ph\u1ea7n c\u00e1c em \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u00ecnh v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec1 xu\u1ea5t xem c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn s\u1edbm, v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u mu\u1ed9n v\u00e0o h\u00f4m sau\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng T\u1ea5n Anh vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea5m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xem c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u mu\u1ed9n \u1edf World Cup 2018 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u thi\u1ec7t th\u00f2i, song to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u1edfi l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7c t\u1ea1i V.League. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb n\u00e0y n\u00f3i th\u00eam: \u201cC\u00e1c em c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn th\u1ee9c r\u00f5 t\u1eadp trung cho V-League m\u1edbi l\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng, xem World Cup c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee9c. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 xem tr\u1ecdn c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00f9 h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n, nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf \u0111\u00fang l\u00e0 thi\u1ec7t th\u00f2i. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay qu\u00e1 d\u00e0y, l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9, n\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e0nh kh\u1eaft khe v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n xem World Cup. Do \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn s\u1edbm l\u00fac 7 gi\u1edd, 8 gi\u1edd t\u1ed1i th\u00ec c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eadp trung xem c\u00f9ng nhau, nh\u01b0ng sau \u0111\u00f3 th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 t\u1ed5 ki\u1ec3m tra \u0111\u1ec3 xem c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00fang lu\u1eadt kh\u00f4ng. CLB kh\u00f4ng cho ph\u00e9p c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u00e1y t\u00ednh b\u1ea3ng, \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 xem b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 vi ph\u1ea1m CLB s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng k\u1ec9 lu\u1eadt n\u1eb7ng tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00f3. Tuy nhi\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u1eb7t tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o \u00fd th\u1ee9c t\u1ef1 gi\u00e1c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c em\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ec1u nay, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ra s\u00e2n v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng t\u1ea1i H\u00f2a Xu\u00e2n. \u1ede 3 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u01b0\u1edbc, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u00f4ng H\u00e0n, v\u00ec th\u1ebf c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb nh\u00e0 b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-shb-da-nang-vs-hagl-17h00-ngay-176-tim-lai-chien-thang-168-188684.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/nhan-dinh-shb-da-nang-vs-hagl-17h00-ngay-176-tim-lai-chien-thang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-shb-da-nang-vs-hagl-17h00-ngay-176-tim-lai-chien-thang-168-188684.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs HAGL (17h00 ng\u00e0y 17/6): T\u00ecm l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng</span><br>\r\nC\u1ea3 SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs HAGL \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Do \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p nhau n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:#081f2c;=\"\" mso-fareast-language:ko\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3659","checkdouble":"188685"},{"date":"08:28 17/06","title":"SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng tr\u00ecnh ngo\u1ea1i binh Thai-League \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p HAGL?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/shb-da-nang-trinh-hang-thaileague-o-tran-gap-hagl.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong tr\u1eadn t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u HAGL t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n H\u00f2a Xu\u00e2n v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u nay, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng HLV Minh Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Yao Hermann Kouassi. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o v\u1eeba chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y sau 7 n\u0103m ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Thai-League.</h2><h2>SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ngo\u1ea1i binh t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Thai-League,\u00a0<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Yao Hermann Kouassi</span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o l\u00fac 17h00 chi\u1ec1u nay, CLB SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c v\u00f2ng 14 V-League tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 g\u1eb7p c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL. Sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u00f4ng H\u00e0n l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, qua \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u00ean BXH.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng tr\u00ecnh ngo\u1ea1i binh Thai-League \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p HAGL  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng tr\u00ecnh ngo\u1ea1i binh Thai-League \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p HAGL  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/shb-da-nang-trinh-hang-thaileague-o-tran-gap-hagl.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u00e2n binh Yao Hermann Kouassi \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p  HAGL?. \u1ea2nh: Bongda.com.vn</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u00f4ng H\u00e0n c\u0169ng s\u1ebd tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0ng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat m\u00e0 h\u1ecd v\u1eeba chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 t\u1eeb Thai-League, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 Yao Hermann Kouassi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kouassi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 7 n\u0103m ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Th\u00e1i Lan. Anh t\u1eebng thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho CLB Air Force Central t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Thai Division League (Thai-League 2) v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2011 v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y l\u00ean ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i Thai-League 1 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2014, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi gia nh\u1eadp Chiangmai, Bangkok v\u00e0 Samut Sakhon.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 cao 1m67 nh\u01b0ng b\u00f9 l\u1ea1i Kouassi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c r\u1ea5t sung m\u00e3n. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y c\u00f2n cho th\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u0103n b\u00e0n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi 61 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong 136 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho CLB Air Force Central, m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 t\u1ec7. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Kouassi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd san s\u1ebb g\u00e1nh n\u1eb7ng c\u00f9ng \u0110\u1ed7 Merlo v\u00e0 H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh, trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh ngo\u1ea1i binh c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 Diogo \u0111ang \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i n\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng sau l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i v\u1edbi 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng \u0111ang g\u1ea5p r\u00fat ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft nh\u01b0 kh\u00e1m s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe v\u00e0 gi\u1ea5y ch\u1ee9ng nh\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf (ITC) \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ecbp \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd Yao Hermann Kouassi \u1edf cu\u1ed9c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n HAGL v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y mai. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n h\u01a1n t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.\u00a0</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-shb-da-nang-vs-hagl-17h00-ngay-176-tim-lai-chien-thang-168-188684.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/nhan-dinh-shb-da-nang-vs-hagl-17h00-ngay-176-tim-lai-chien-thang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-shb-da-nang-vs-hagl-17h00-ngay-176-tim-lai-chien-thang-168-188684.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs HAGL (17h00 ng\u00e0y 17/6): T\u00ecm l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng</span><br>\r\nC\u1ea3 SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs HAGL \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Do \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p nhau n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";=\"\" mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:#081f2c;mso-fareast-language:=\"\" ko\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3658","checkdouble":"188687"},{"date":"08:46 17/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh S\u00e0i G\u00f2n vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i 19h00 ng\u00e0y 17/6 (V-League 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/17/nhan-dinh-sai-gon-vs-ha-noi-19h00-ngay-176-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>S\u00e0i G\u00f2n vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i l\u00fac 19h00 ng\u00e0y 17/6 (V\u00f2ng 14 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh S\u00e0i G\u00f2n vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i 19h00 ng\u00e0y 176 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh S\u00e0i G\u00f2n vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i 19h00 ng\u00e0y 176 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/saigon-hanoi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">S\u00e0i G\u00f2n vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>\u00a0</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 vs Thanh H\u00f3a: 1-2</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>T\u00e2m tr\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f4ng vui, khi h\u1ecd v\u1eeba tr\u1eafng tay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Thi\u00ean Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u1edf v\u00f2ng 13. C\u0169ng v\u00ec tr\u1eadn thua \u1ea5y, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i r\u1edbt xu\u1ed1ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u00e1p ch\u00f3t tr\u00ean BXH. Th\u1ebf n\u00ean, cu\u1ed9c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng c\u00e0ng th\u00eam ph\u1ea7n kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n l\u1eabn \u00e1p l\u1ef1c cho ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch \u0111ang gi\u1eef k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c khi b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ea3 13 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, n\u00ean h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 mu\u1ed1n th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1ea5y b\u1ecb ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 ngay tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1. Tuy nhi\u00ean, trong ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00f9i, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC th\u01b0\u1eddng r\u1ea5t bi\u1ebft si\u1ebft ch\u1eb7t tay nhau \u0111\u1ec3 \u201ct\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sinh trong c\u1eeda t\u1eed\u201d. N\u00f3i th\u1ebf, v\u00ec \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t ngoan c\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC, n\u00ean hy v\u1ecdng h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf cu\u1ed9c t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u chi\u1ec1u nay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn n\u00e0y c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1edf h\u1eefu l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 quay l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Da Sylva v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 t\u1ef1 tin h\u01a1n trong vi\u1ec7c t\u00ecm \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH D\u1ef0 KI\u1ebeN<br>\r\nS\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC: \u0110\u1ee9c An, Ho\u00e0ng Qu\u1ea3ng, Qu\u1ed1c Long, Th\u00e0nh T\u00edn, Tr\u1ea7n V\u0169, Ti\u1ebfn Duy, Xu\u00e2n D\u01b0\u01a1ng, V\u0103n Tri\u1ec1n, Ho\u00e0ng Thi\u00ean, Dugary, Da Sylva.<br>\r\nH\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC: V\u0103n C\u00f4ng, V\u0103n Ki\u00ean, V\u0103n H\u1eadu, Duy M\u1ea1nh, Duy Kh\u00e1nh, Th\u00e0nh L\u01b0\u01a1ng, Moses, V\u0103n \u0110\u1ea1i, H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng, Quang H\u1ea3i, Samson.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Bongdaplus.vn</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3657","checkdouble":"188690"},{"date":"14:59 16/06","title":"Hai sao tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh b\u1ecb b\u1eaft v\u00ec c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c c\u01b0\u1ee1ng b\u1ee9c c\u00f4 g\u00e1i tr\u1ebb","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/16/hai-sao-tre-nguoi-anh-bi-bat-vi-cao-buoc-cuong-buc-co-gai-tre.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Hai sao tr\u1ebb Reeco Hackett-Fairchild v\u00e0 Karlan Ahearne-Grant c\u1ee7a Charlton \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb b\u1eaft t\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00ec c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng xxx m\u1ed9t c\u00f4 g\u00e1i 19 tu\u1ed5i.</h2>V\u00e0o h\u00f4m qua, b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Hackett-Fairchild v\u00e0 Ahearne-Grant \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb c\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u1eaft \u1edf m\u1ed9t kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n t\u1ea1i Cala de Bou, g\u1ea7n khu ngh\u1ec9 m\u00e1t San Antonio t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea3o Ibiza. Hackett-Fairchild v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng 26 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00e1c b\u1ecb b\u1eaft v\u00ec c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t c\u00f4 g\u00e1i 19 tu\u1ed5i.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/charlton.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, Ahearne-Grant \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u0169ng b\u1ecb b\u1eaft v\u00ec nghi ng\u1edd ph\u1ea1m t\u1ed9i k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean nh\u01b0ng sau khi th\u1ea9m v\u1ea5n, anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho ph\u00e9p r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng, Ahearne-Grant v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i s\u1ee9 qu\u00e1n T\u00e2y Ban Nha t\u1ea1i London v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 1 v\u00e0 15 h\u00e0ng th\u00e1ng.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHackett-Fairchild v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i v\u1eabn b\u1ecb gi\u1eef nguy\u00ean c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u00ecnh d\u1ee5c. H\u1ecd ch\u01b0a b\u1ecb bu\u1ed9c t\u1ed9i b\u1edfi theo lu\u1eadt T\u00e2y Ban Nha, c\u00e1o tr\u1ea1ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1edd x\u00e9t x\u1eed t\u1ea1i t\u00f2a \u00e1n. Hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00e0y s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea3o Ibiza v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec7n \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 2 l\u1ea7n/th\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i t\u00f2a \u00e1n \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. N\u1ebfu b\u1ecb bu\u1ed9c t\u1ed9i, Hackett-Fairchild v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng l\u1ea1 m\u1eb7t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u0129nh \u00e1n 15 n\u0103m t\u00f9.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nV\u1ee5 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u00ecnh d\u1ee5c x\u1ea3y ra sau khi Hackett-Fairchild v\u00e0 Ahearne-Grant r\u1eddi qu\u00e1n bar Ocean Beach \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh b\u1edfi Wayne Lineker, anh trai c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Gary Lineker. C\u00f4 g\u00e1i 19 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n \u201c\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0\u201d \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd c\u00f9ng b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Charlton tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n Cala de Bou. Th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng, b\u1ed1 m\u1eb9 c\u1ee7a c\u00f4 g\u00e1i 19 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e1o c\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t sau khi bi\u1ebft chuy\u1ec7n g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra v\u1edbi con g\u00e1i h\u1ecd.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/charlton1.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSau v\u1ee5 vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y, CLB Charlton \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o: \u201cCLB \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin v\u00e0 \u0111ang xem x\u00e9t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00e0y. Do cu\u1ed9c \u0111i\u1ec1u tra \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn th\u00eam g\u00ec v\u1ec1 v\u1ee5 vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y\u201d. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nAhearne-Grant l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Charlton khi 17 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 9/2014. Anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 h\u01a1n 60 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho CLB t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 h\u1ea1ng Nh\u00ec Anh. Ahearne-Grant c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i cho U17, U18 v\u00e0 U19 Anh. V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Hackett-Fairchild, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft Charlton v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 8/2017 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 2 b\u00e0n trong 12 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n.<br /></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3653","checkdouble":"188641"},{"date":"13:49 16/06","title":"T\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ed1t ph\u00e1o s\u00e1ng t\u00e1i di\u1ec5n: Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t n\u1eb7ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/13/tinh-trang-dot-phao-sang-tai-dien-nhieu-doi-bong-bi-phat-nang.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt VFF m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t cho c\u00e1c CLB do \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00e1i di\u1ec5n t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ed1t ph\u00e1o s\u00e1ng tr\u00ean c\u00e1c kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i \u1edf v\u00f2ng 13 V-League 2018.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u2018chung k\u1ebft s\u1edbm\u2019 gi\u1eefa CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 13 V-League, sau khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft ghi b\u00e0n \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft \u0111\u01b0a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ph\u00e1o s\u00e1ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c C\u0110V \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 n\u00e9m xu\u1ed1ng s\u00e2n nh\u01b0 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 \u0103n m\u1eebng.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ed1t ph\u00e1o s\u00e1ng t\u00e1i di\u1ec5n Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t n\u1eb7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ed1t ph\u00e1o s\u00e1ng t\u00e1i di\u1ec5n Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t n\u1eb7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/13/IMG_0792_resize.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>T\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ed1t ph\u00e1o s\u00e1ng t\u00e1i di\u1ec5n \u1edf v\u00f2ng 13 V-League</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y, BTC s\u00e2n H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a VFF. Theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, BTC tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a CLB b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i 50.000.000\u0111 (N\u0103m m\u01b0\u01a1i tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng) do \u0111\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed1t ph\u00e1o s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 13, di\u1ec5n ra ng\u00e0y 13/6/2018 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, CLB H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng c\u1ee7a HLV Tr\u01b0\u01a1ng Vi\u1ec7t Ho\u00e0ng c\u00f2n nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn t\u1eeb ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt VFF. Theo \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea5t C\u1ea3ng b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 60 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng do \u0111\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng c\u00e1c C\u0110V \u0111\u1ed1t ph\u00e1o s\u00e1ng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa hai CLB SLNA v\u00e0 H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng t\u1ea1i l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 13, tr\u00ean s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng Vinh, Ngh\u1ec7 An.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean CLB H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t ti\u1ec1n b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 qu\u00e1 kh\u00edch c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c C\u0110V. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea5t C\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb v\u1ea1 l\u00e2y b\u1edfi chuy\u1ec7n c\u00e1c C\u0110V li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed1t ph\u00e1o s\u00e1ng tr\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i d\u00f9 h\u1ecd thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 hay s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c c\u0169ng \u2018chung s\u1ed1 ph\u1eadn ch\u1ecbu ph\u1ea1t\u2019 v\u1edbi H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00e0 H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng l\u00e0 CLB Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh. D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ed1t ph\u00e1o s\u00e1ng song BTC s\u00e2n Thi\u00ean Tr\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 ch\u1ea1y xu\u1ed1ng s\u00e2n v\u00e0 n\u00e9m nhi\u1ec1u chai, l\u1ecd xu\u1ed1ng s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa hai CLB b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Nam c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 n\u00ean s\u1ef1 ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c C\u0110V Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u nay m\u00e0 chi\u1ec1u mai 17/6, v\u00f2ng 14 s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c th\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee9c c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 th\u00ec b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc c\u0169ng \u0111\u1eebng qu\u00ean theo d\u00f5i c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i V-League 2018 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Bongda24h t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m ph\u1ea7n h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn, k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sao-hagl-choi-xau-chinh-thuc-nhan-an-phat-nang-cua-vff-168-188628.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/sao-hagl-choi-xau-chinh-thuc-nhan-an-phat-nang-cua-vff.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sao-hagl-choi-xau-chinh-thuc-nhan-an-phat-nang-cua-vff-168-188628.html\">Sao HAGL ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t n\u1eb7ng c\u1ee7a VFF</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt VFF \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 c\u00e1c \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t cho c\u00e1c CLB sau v\u00f2ng 13 V-League, \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n H\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a CLB HAGL b\u1ecb c\u1ea5m thi \u0111\u1ea5u 3 tr\u1eadn sau h\u00e0nh...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3652","checkdouble":"188631"},{"date":"14:06 16/06","title":"Sao tr\u1ebb B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/sao-tre-binh-duong-bat-ngo-vi-duoc-lot-vao-danh-sach-tham-du-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o CLB b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb Nguy\u1ec5n Thanh Th\u1ea3o \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Park Hang Seo b\u1ed5 sung v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch s\u01a1 b\u1ed9 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Thanh Th\u1ea3o b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Thanh Th\u1ea3o b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/HLV-Park-Hang-Seo-trao-co-hoi-cho-cau-thu-tre-B.Binh-Duong-tai-Asiad-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Thanh Th\u1ea3o (s\u1ed1 3) l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o 'm\u1eaft xanh' c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho Asiad 2018 di\u1ec5n ra tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Indonesia v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 8 t\u1edbi, trong th\u1eddi gian v\u1eeba qua HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c \u0111i \u2018vi h\u00e0nh\u2019 tr\u00ean c\u00e1c s\u00e2n b\u00f3ng kh\u1eafp c\u1ea3 n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u00e0i cho \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tham d\u1ef1 \u00c1 v\u1eadn h\u1ed9i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, th\u1ea7y Park \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5m m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 Nguy\u1ec5n Thanh Th\u1ea3o. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean Thanh Th\u1ea3o v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch s\u01a1 b\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Indonesia. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi, CLB B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1ebd cung c\u1ea5p c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u1ec3 VFF chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho Thanh Th\u1ea3o c\u00e1c gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i khi l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n. Vi\u1ec7c Thanh Th\u1ea3o l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u1edbn v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 v\u00e0 gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n trong n\u01b0\u1edbc, b\u1edfi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n m\u1edbi. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady n\u1ebfu nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u1edbi B.B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u00ec r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00fd do g\u1ecdi Thanh Th\u1ea3o c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. M\u00f9a n\u00e0y, Thanh Th\u1ea3o \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 10 tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i V.League 2018 v\u00e0 ghi 2 b\u00e0n cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea5t Th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch s\u01a1 b\u1ed9 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n th\u01b0\u1edfng cho nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c kh\u00f4ng m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00e1 m\u0129 mi\u1ec1u n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi bi\u1ebft tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n, sao tr\u1ebb B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ea5n kh\u1edfi. Anh n\u00f3i: \"T\u00f4i v\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0 B.B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean, t\u00f4i th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 h\u01a1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Song b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n n\u1eefa\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ec1u mai 17/6, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Thanh Th\u1ea3o v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1eb7p SLNA t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 14 V-League tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Vinh. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng cho m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trong nh\u00f3m d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea5t Th\u1ee7.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/tinh-trang-dot-phao-sang-tai-dien-nhieu-doi-bong-bi-phat-nang-168-188631.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/13/tinh-trang-dot-phao-sang-tai-dien-nhieu-doi-bong-bi-phat-nang.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/tinh-trang-dot-phao-sang-tai-dien-nhieu-doi-bong-bi-phat-nang-168-188631.html\">T\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ed1t ph\u00e1o s\u00e1ng t\u00e1i di\u1ec5n: Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t n\u1eb7ng</span><br>\r\nBan k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt VFF m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t cho c\u00e1c CLB do \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00e1i di\u1ec5n t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ed1t ph\u00e1o s\u00e1ng tr\u00ean c\u00e1c kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i \u1edf v\u00f2ng 13 V-League 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sao-hagl-choi-xau-chinh-thuc-nhan-an-phat-nang-cua-vff-168-188628.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/sao-hagl-choi-xau-chinh-thuc-nhan-an-phat-nang-cua-vff.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sao-hagl-choi-xau-chinh-thuc-nhan-an-phat-nang-cua-vff-168-188628.html\">Sao HAGL ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t n\u1eb7ng c\u1ee7a VFF</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt VFF \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 c\u00e1c \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t cho c\u00e1c CLB sau v\u00f2ng 13 V-League, \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n H\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a CLB HAGL b\u1ecb c\u1ea5m thi \u0111\u1ea5u 3 tr\u1eadn sau h\u00e0nh...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3651","checkdouble":"188634"},{"date":"14:18 16/06","title":"Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u2018h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\u2019 c\u1ee7a FLC Thanh H\u00f3a ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/them-mot-cau-thu-hang-thai-cua-flc-thanh-hoa-chinh-thuc-co-ben-do-moi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, BL\u0110 CLB SLNA \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ho\u00e0ng V\u0103n B\u00ecnh cho giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018 theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1eeb FLC Thanh H\u00f3a.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ho\u00e0ng V\u0103n B\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a FLC Thanh H\u00f3a ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ho\u00e0ng V\u0103n B\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a FLC Thanh H\u00f3a ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/8/tien-ve-Hoang-Van-Binh-cua-FLC-Thanh-Hoa-chinh-thuc-co-ben-do-moi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ho\u00e0ng V\u0103n B\u00ecnh tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i kho\u00e1c \u00e1o CLB SLNA</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ho\u00e0ng V\u0103n B\u00ecnh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thu\u1ed9c di\u1ec7n thanh l\u00fd \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i FLC Thanh H\u00f3a. Sau khi BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y, V\u0103n B\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n hai v\u00e0 anh nhanh ch\u00f3ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng SLNA.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t th\u00ec h\u00f4m qua (15/6), \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ho\u00e0ng V\u0103n B\u00ecnh cho giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018 theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1eeb FLC Thanh H\u00f3a.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sinh n\u0103m 1989 t\u1ea1i Qu\u1ef3nh L\u01b0u, V\u0103n B\u00ecnh c\u00f9ng l\u1ee9a v\u1edbi Tr\u1ecdng Ho\u00e0ng, \u00c2u V\u0103n Ho\u00e0n,\u2026 - nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i 1 SLNA t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2007... B\u1eb1ng n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, anh t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0110T U20 Vi\u1ec7t Nam khi m\u1edbi 18 tu\u1ed5i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u0103m 2011, Ho\u00e0ng V\u0103n B\u00ecnh l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tham d\u1ef1 SEA Games. C\u0169ng trong qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf SLNA, V\u0103n B\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 3 l\u1ea7n n\u00e2ng C\u00fap c\u00f9ng CLB (V.League 2011, C\u00fap QG 2010 v\u00e0 si\u00eau c\u00fap 2011).<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec th\u1ebf, s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a V\u0103n B\u00ecnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft cho tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a SLNA trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1. L\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 \u0111ang ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng v\u1edbi Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n, n\u00ean vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 gi\u00fap s\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a V\u0103n B\u00ecnh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sao-tre-binh-duong-bat-ngo-vi-duoc-lot-vao-danh-sach-tham-du-asiad-2018-168-188634.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/sao-tre-binh-duong-bat-ngo-vi-duoc-lot-vao-danh-sach-tham-du-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sao-tre-binh-duong-bat-ngo-vi-duoc-lot-vao-danh-sach-tham-du-asiad-2018-168-188634.html\">Sao tr\u1ebb B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o CLB b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb Nguy\u1ec5n Thanh Th\u1ea3o \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Park Hang Seo b\u1ed5 sung v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch s\u01a1 b\u1ed9 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sao-hagl-choi-xau-chinh-thuc-nhan-an-phat-nang-cua-vff-168-188628.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/sao-hagl-choi-xau-chinh-thuc-nhan-an-phat-nang-cua-vff.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sao-hagl-choi-xau-chinh-thuc-nhan-an-phat-nang-cua-vff-168-188628.html\">Sao HAGL ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t n\u1eb7ng c\u1ee7a VFF</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt VFF \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 c\u00e1c \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t cho c\u00e1c CLB sau v\u00f2ng 13 V-League, \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n H\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a CLB HAGL b\u1ecb c\u1ea5m thi \u0111\u1ea5u 3 tr\u1eadn sau h\u00e0nh...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u00a0Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3650","checkdouble":"188635"},{"date":"14:54 16/06","title":"HLV Riedl n\u00f3i ph\u0169 v\u1ec1 gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 World Cup c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/hlv-riedl-noi-phu-ve-giac-mo-world-cup-cua-bong-da-viet.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>B\u00ean l\u1ec1 VCK World Cup 2018, c\u1ef1u HLV \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u00f4ng Alfred Riedl \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng cho r\u1eb1ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u01a1 t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi n\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 suy ngh\u0129 nh\u01b0 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.</h2><h2>HLV Riedl: B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1eebng m\u01a1 World Cup n\u1ebfu c\u1ee9 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y!</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m qua \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 \u1edf c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb nh\u01b0 vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i U19 v\u00e0 U23 \u0111\u1ec1u thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i VCK ch\u00e2u \u00c1, trong \u0111\u00f3 U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f2n gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 tham d\u1ef1 VCK U20 World Cup.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Riedl n\u00f3i ph\u0169 v\u1ec1 gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 World Cup c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Riedl n\u00f3i ph\u0169 v\u1ec1 gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 World Cup c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/1-1529073604-width500height333.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Riedl kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh th\u1ef1c t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, theo \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a HLV Riedl th\u00ec ch\u1eebng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u01a1 t\u01b0\u1edfng ra s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, khi m\u00e0 su\u1ed1t 10 n\u0103m qua, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1edf \u0110TQG Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean t\u1edd Zing.vn, \u00f4ng Riedl \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i r\u00f5 h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y: \u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 trong h\u01a1n 10 n\u0103m qua. G\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t l\u1edbn n\u00e0o gi\u1eefa \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a n\u0103m 2007 v\u00e0 n\u0103m 2018. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00f4i th\u1ea5y b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn thi\u1ebfu n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c trong c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ef1 ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, Vi\u1ec7t Nam ph\u1ea3i th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb khu v\u1ef1c. Sau \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c. Nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u1edbi t\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c World Cup.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f2n hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh ho\u1eb7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho vi\u1ec7c tham d\u1ef1 World Cup. C\u00e1c b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd m\u1ea5t bao l\u00e2u \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1edbi C\u00fap th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u01b0? \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 v\u1eabn ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n trong ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a HLV Riedl ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c khi m\u00e0 l\u00fac n\u00e0y b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn \u0111ang loay hoay t\u00ecm l\u1ed1i tho\u00e1t cho b\u00e0i to\u00e1n l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1, \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 10 n\u0103m qua ch\u00fang ta lu\u00f4n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch, l\u1ed9 tr\u00ecnh d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n c\u00f9ng s\u1ef1 chung tay c\u1ee7a t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c b\u00ean th\u00ec gi\u1ea5c m\u1ed9ng World Cup c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi s\u1ed1 su\u1ea5t tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2026.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3649","checkdouble":"188640"}]}